As the part of the project development of UI editor for monitoring video streams from security cameras was needed. It consists of 2 independent systems, one for creating UI projects and the other for exporting those projects into fully functional web pages. First part is developed in generic way, which means that output of the system can be used to produce not only web pages, but also standalone applications. UI project describes the UI elements, their functionalities and appearances.

•   Developed the architecture of the UI editor based on the requirements of project managers and WeMB company. •   Developed and deployed the system in the Tomcat server. Backend was developed using Java Server Pages.
